Get Property Values for Data Commons Nodes

Source: R/node.R
dc_get_property_values.Rd

A convenience wrapper around dc_get_node() to retrieve all property values for the specified nodes. This is equivalent to calling dc_get_node() with expression = "<-".

dc_get_property_values(
  nodes,
  properties = "name",
  api_key = Sys.getenv("DATACOMMONS_API_KEY"),
  base_url = Sys.getenv("DATACOMMONS_BASE_URL", unset =
    "https://api.datacommons.org/v2/"),
  return_type = "json"
)

Arguments

nodes

A character vector of terms to resolve.

properties

A character vector of properties (e.g. "name", "latitude", "all")

api_key

Your Data Commons API key. If not provided, uses the environment variable DATACOMMONS_API_KEY.

base_url

The base URL of the Data Commons API. Defaults to the public endpoint. For custom deployments, must end with /core/api/v2/.

return_type

Return format: either "list" (parsed R object) or "json" (JSON string).

Value

A list containing the requested property values for each node. The structure depends on the properties requested and follows the same format as dc_get_node().

Examples

# Get the name property (default)
dc_get_property_values(nodes = "country/USA")
#> [1] "{\"data\":{\"country/USA\":{\"arcs\":{\"name\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"United States of America\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"United States\"}]}}}}}"

# Get a specific property
dc_get_property_values(nodes = "country/USA", properties = "latitude")
#> [1] "{\"data\":{\"country/USA\":{\"arcs\":{\"latitude\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"37.09024\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"39.828175\"}]}}}}}"

# Get multiple specific properties
dc_get_property_values(
  nodes = c("geoId/06085", "geoId/06087"),
  properties = c("name", "latitude", "longitude")
)
#> [1] "{\"data\":{\"geoId/06087\":{\"arcs\":{\"name\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"Santa Cruz County\"}]},\"latitude\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"37.012347\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"37.03\"}]},\"longitude\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"-122.007789\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"-122.01\"}]}}},\"geoId/06085\":{\"arcs\":{\"name\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"Santa Clara County\"}]},\"latitude\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"37.221614\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"37.36\"}]},\"longitude\":{\"nodes\":[{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"-121.68954\"},{\"provenanceId\":\"dc/base/WikidataOtherIdGeos\",\"value\":\"-121.97\"}]}}}}}"
